---

FINAL DEFINITION

Legacy Persistence Economy is a decentralized persistence protocol that transforms outbound blockchain activity into irreversible contribution history, forming a cross-chain economic system where identity, trust, and value emerge from persistent participation and socially recognized contribution lineage rather than custodial ownership alone.
